---
---

<section class="spaced why-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="blue-dot"></span>The problem</span>
      <h2><span class="primary-blue">PDF parsing is misery.</span> <span class="accent">We made it someone else's problem</span></h2>
      <p>Three things every team building invoice features ends up doing badly. We do them well, once, for everyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="why-grid">
      <article class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="14" x2="13" y2="18"/>
            <line x1="13" y1="14" x2="9" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-title">Parsing PDFs from email</h3>
        <p class="why-body">Every vendor sends a different layout. Regex breaks. LLMs burn tokens reading mailroom data. We extract structured fields server-side and hand you JSON.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/>
            <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-title">Detecting duplicates</h3>
        <p class="why-body">The same invoice arrives twice — forwarded, resent, attached to a thread reply. Three-signal dedup (hash, number, amount) flags conflicts instead of silently merging.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-title">Trusting what arrived</h3>
        <p class="why-body">Was this invoice tampered with between vendor and your stack? Every delivery carries an ed25519 signature, replay-safe, TLS-only. You verify once and stop worrying.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
